cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CVPR 

The paper discusses dense image alignment using data-driven priors and optimization techniques. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also focuses on 3D rigid motion estimation tasks, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper presents experiments on image-to-pose regression, which is a common topic in computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CVPR) sub-category.
